metadata.name: Galaxy Guardian - Prototype Edition
metadata.description:
This is an original piece of AI generated art created by DALL路E 2.

DALL路E 2 is an AI system that can create realistic images & art from a description in natural language.

DALL路E 2 helps us understand how advanced AI systems see & understand our world, which is critical to our mission of creating AI that benefits humanity.

10% of profits made from sales of this NFT go to PhygiEd programs. These workshops and educational resources are aimed at providing equitable opportunities in Web3 & The Metaverse to diverse audiences.
